  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Eiger Lodge is offered on a half board basis.</p>
<p>A hot and cold buffet breakfast is served each morning between 7.30am and 9.30am, offering local and regional products and ingredients.</p>
<p>Guests choosing half board will have a three course evening meal at Restaurant Grund, a local restaurant, about 200 metres away from Eiger Lodge.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Eiger Lodge hotel provides a base that connects you to the surrounding mountains, through the décor, the views, the regional delicacies in the meals and the fact the hotel is situated right next to the main gondola - it is the ideal hotel for your ski holiday.</p>
<h2>Easy access to the ski area</h2>
<p>If you want to be one of the first on the mountain each morning, then the Eiger Lodge is perfectly located for you. It's only a few minutes walk to the Grindelwald Terminal where the speedy new Eiger Express Gondola will take you up to the Eiger Glacier in no time at all. The Grindelwald Grund Station is a couple of minutes in the other direction, so you're in a great place to explore the whole area.</p>
<h2>Convenience </h2>
<p>The Eiger Lodge is new to town and therefore you can expect clean, modern and well equipped rooms. Our rooms are located in the new 'Chic' part of the lodge, so all have shower and WC. A nice buffet breakfast is included and served each morning. The lodge doesn't have extensive facilities, but if you're out for most of the day and need a comfortable room to come back to, then look no further.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
